{"tid":2390294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中原地產後勤員工今年獲加薪2.5%","createTime":"2021-02-01T12:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T12:40:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67e91dd9965ad3ad0ee033c10f6a224bb99b575f","tid":2390294,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573512-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573512-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=a0ffdee1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573512-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a1c1358a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573512-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中原地產表示，去年全年香港住宅部營業額逾38億元，4季皆錄得盈利，第4季全線後勤員工獲發花紅0.3個月，主任級或以上0.46個月，連續47個季度獲發花紅，將於本周五發放。全年全線後勤獲發1.19個月花紅，主任級或以上1.79個月。全線後勤今年加薪2.5%。<br />\n<br />\n住宅部總裁陳永傑指出，今年1月樓市已呈現小陽春格局，初步結算1月佣金3.56億元，按月上升36%，創7個月新高。<br />\n<br />\n陳永傑說，今年農曆新年買家業主因抗疫被迫留港，2月多個新盤緊接登場，預料小陽春將延續至新年後，2月一手成交或達2千宗。"},{"pid":"c558b1014f2a96d306f015b90a7d124dae37a191","tid":2390294,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:40:07.000Z","msg":"如果10萬月薪加成2500蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02dfca982271069f267db198255af7e30048d8a5","tid":2390294,"uid":13867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:40:18.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂！"}]}